OL,7,FIt's aimed at tackling bias in the
OL,8,Fjustice system and cutting
OL,9,Freoffending, and highlights the need
OL,10,Ffor pre-sentence reports to give more
OL,11,Fdetails about the offender before
OL,12,Fthey're sentenced.
OL,14,FMagistrates and judges would have to
OL,15,Fconsult the report before deciding
OL,16,Fwhether to imprison the person and how
OL,17,Flong for.
