OL,4,Cgovernment and the Sentencing Council
OL,5,Cclashing?
OL,7,FAs soon as the guidance was published,
OL,8,FMahmood immediately dismissed it as
OL,9,F"two-tier sentencing", asking the
OL,10,Fcouncil to remove all the groups of
OL,11,Fpeople listed under the pre-sentence
OL,12,Freport guidelines and to use a wider
OL,13,Fclause instead.
OL,15,FBut when they refused and then back-
OL,16,Ftracked slightly agreeing to delay the
OL,17,Fnew guidance, the government brought
OL,18,Fforward emergency legislation to block
OL,19,Fit.
