OL,3,C'Two-tier justice': Why are the
OL,4,Cgovernment and the Sentencing Council
OL,5,Cclashing?
OL,7,FThe new law introduced on Tuesday
OL,8,Fwould ban the Sentencing Council from
OL,9,Fmaking guidelines about pre-sentence
OL,10,Freports with specific reference to an
OL,11,Foffender's personal characteristics.
OL,13,FMahmood told the Commons: "My view is
OL,14,Fthat despite the noble intentions
OL,15,Fbehind them in attempting to address
OL,16,Finequalities in our justice system,
OL,17,Fthese guidelines sacrifice too much."
