OL,3,C'Two-tier justice': Why are the
OL,4,Cgovernment and the Sentencing Council
OL,5,Cclashing?
OL,7,FThere has been lots of criticism of
OL,8,Fthe guidelines, saying they create a
OL,9,F"two-tier" justice system, where
OL,10,Fpeople from certain groups are given
OL,11,Fpreferential treatment.
OL,13,FBut many people argue there is already
OL,14,Fa "two-tier" system, with people from
OL,15,Fethnic minorities and other
OL,16,Fmarginalised groups overrepresented in
OL,17,Fprisons and experiencing worse
OL,18,Foutcomes in the justice system.
